Package simu.model.entity

Class Simulation

java.lang.Object
simu.model.entity.Simulation
@Entity public class Simulation extends Object
The Simulation class represents a simulation in the simulation. A simulation is created when the user starts a new simulation. It contains the user-provided values and the calculated values. The calculated values are updated during the simulation.
